                <formatted-text>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#555555' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='11' underline='true'>Key Takeaways</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='10'>Shorts drove the most reach, making them the strongest format for broad audience exposure.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='10'>Interview/Press generated the highest discussion rate and strongest sentiment, but lower engagement efficiency.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='10'>Playoff Stakes and Star Player themes accounted for most views, showing the value of high-stakes and player-driven storylines.</run>
